Package: dlrm
Version: 1.0
Date: 2009-09-14
Title: Dynamic Linear Regression Model
Author: Maarten Speekenbrink <m.speekenbrink@ucl.ac.uk>
Maintainer: Maarten Speekenbrink <m.speekenbrink@ucl.ac.uk>
Depends: R (>= 2.8.0), nlme, numDeriv
Description: This package implements the estimation of a dynamic linear
    regression model by a Kalman filter/smoother, using the EM algorithm for
    (hyper-)parameter estimation.
License: GPL (>=2)
URL: http://psychol.ucl.ac.uk/m.speekenbrink/software
